Products – Monster Energy® Drinks Segment
Monster Energy® Drinks - a line of carbonated energy drinks. Our Monster Energy® drinks
contain vitamins, minerals, nutrients, herbs and other ingredients (collectively, “supplement ingredients”)
and are marketed through our full service distributor network. We offer the following energy drinks under
the Monster Energy® drink product line: Monster Energy®, Lo-Carb Monster Energy®, Monster
Assault®, Monster Energy® Fury®, Juice Monster® Khaos®, Juice Monster® Ripper®, Juice Monster®
