Ultra Red®, Monster Energy Ultra Black®, Monster Energy Ultra Paradise®, Monster Energy Ultra
Sunrise®, Monster Energy Ultra Citron®, Monster Energy Ultra Violet®, Monster Energy® Gronk,
Monster Energy® Valentino Rossi and Monster Energy® Lewis Hamilton 44.
