26term capacity may not be available for such products either at commercially reasonable rates and/or costs
and/or within a reasonably short time period, if at all. In addition, recently there has been a consolidation
of co-packers.  If we are unable to maintain good relationships with our largest co-packers, or if our costs
of co-packing increase, our business, financial condition and results of operations could be adversely
affected.
We rely on bottlers and distributors to distribute our products. If we are unable to maintain good
relationships with our existing bottlers and distributors and/or secure such bottlers and distributors, our
