2.          REVENUE RECOGNITION
Revenues are accounted for in accordance with ASC 606 “Revenue from Contracts with
Consumers” for the years ended December 31, 2019 and 2018. For the year ended December 31, 2017,
revenues were accounted for under prior accounting guidance, ASC 605 “Revenue Recognition.”
