Level 2 within the fair value hierarchy.  The Company’s valuation of its Level 1 investments, which
include money market funds, is based on quoted market prices in active markets for identical securities.
The Company’s valuation of its Level 2 investments, which include municipal securities, commercial
paper, U.S. treasuries, certificates of deposit, VRDNs and U.S. government agency securities, is based on
other observable inputs, specifically a market approach which utilizes valuation models, pricing
